# BLOCK PRISMA DATABASE AND MIGRATION FILES, BUT ALLOW SCHEMA
# Block database files
*.db
*.db-journal
*.db-shm
*.db-wal
**/dev.db
**/dev.db-journal
**/dev.db-shm
**/dev.db-wal

# Block migration files
**/migrations
**/migrations/**

# Block Prisma CLI and tools
**/@prisma/cli
**/@prisma/cli/**
**/prisma-cli
**/prisma-cli/**

# ALLOW Prisma schema file (needed for client generation)
!prisma/schema.prisma

# ALLOW pre-generated Prisma client
!node_modules/@prisma/client
!node_modules/@prisma/client/**
